imdb.plot outline: Sports commentary with a comedic twist starring Dan LeBatard, his father Gonzalo, and sportswriter Bomani Jones. They satirize video clips from all sports and interview an eclectic mix of athletes, rappers and celebs. Gonzalo is the unintended star with his affinity for rap music and his old Cuban-man pronunciations of names and terms. Contrasted with Dan's witty opinions and Bomani's smooth erudition, Gonzalo has a great time poking fun at and holding his own with all the stars.
